uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.motor

Enum ISlotOps

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ISlotOps>
      • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.motor.ISlotOps
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ISlotOps>

    public enum ISlotOps
extends java.lang.Enum<ISlotOps>
    Represents the types of update operation connected with instance-level slots that can be performed as the result of reasoning.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      NONE
      No slot-related updates.
      SLOTS
      Updates of slot-sets on relevant frames, and/or value-types and other attributes for specific slots.
      SLOTS_AND_VALUES
      Both SLOTS and VALUES.
      VALUES
      Updates of fixed values for relevant slots.
